title: 339: Jess & Evan’s Dating Story + New Year’s Resolutions

description:
First The Broads chat about their 2022 resolutions! Then it’s time for an episode (recorded almost 3 YEARS AGO) re-release where Bekah interviews Jess and Evan about how they met, started dating in high school, jealousy, dishonesty, breaking up, rebounds, loving yourself, growing even when it hurts, and much more!
